  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a6db61ac296f850429f2dc6daef8dd23, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dick Letter
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  LetterText: "I\u2019ve admired you for a long time, but now I want to make you
    mine. There is a gala tonight that we\u2019ll both be attending. You\u2019ll
    have to find me in the crowd, I like playing hard to get\u2026 Ask the notable
    guest at the party, I\u2019ll be one of them. Here some stuff to look out for:\r\n\r\nI\u2019m
    sure there will be lots of dancing, but you won\u2019t see me on the dance floor!
    I\u2019m a terrible dancer, maybe you could teach me someday? The person you
    are looking for has two left feet\u2026\r\n\r\nIn this world you have to work
    to get what you want, whatever it takes. I value courage in a person more than
    anything! Your secret lover is a person who likes when people are brave\u2026\r\n\r\nThere\u2019s
    two thing that separates us in this world\u2026 cats or dogs? I\u2019m a total
    dog lover, so find someone who speaks about their doggie fondly\u2026\r\n\r\nSending
    this letter is a bit scary, since I\u2019m a bit shy about romance\u2026 I wont
    turn you down if you ask me out, but I might get a bit flustered. Find someone
    who\u2019s a bit shy around flirting\u2026\r\n\r\nI promise I\u2019ll be the
    only one who matches this exact description, but talk to as many people as possible.
    Some people may have one or more matching interests\u2026"
  rightAnswer: 1
  hintKills: 080000000700000005000000
